OL,3,CThe Truro lottery winner using #13.5m
OL,4,Cjackpot for good deeds
OL,6,FA lottery winner who banked more than
OL,7,F#13 million has said he enjoys using
OL,8,Fhis good fortune to make other
OL,9,Fpeople's lives better.
OL,11,FPeter Congdon, from Truro, scooped
OL,12,F#13.5 million pounds in May 2015 in a
OL,13,Flottery rollover, changing his life
OL,14,Fforever.
OL,16,FAs the National Lottery celebrates
OL,17,Fit's 30th anniversary, Mr Congdon has
OL,18,Fbeen telling ITV West Country how he
OL,19,Fhas been spending his millions.
