OL,3,CThe Truro lottery winner using #13.5m
OL,4,Cjackpot for good deeds
OL,6,FLike many big winners, the 76-year-old
OL,7,Ftreated himself to a luxury car for
OL,8,Fhis first purchase.
OL,10,FHe bought a Bentley Continental, which
OL,11,Fhe now uses to offer free rides to
OL,12,Fpeople in need including brides going
OL,13,Fto their weddings, teens going to prom
OL,14,For people facing the end of their
OL,15,Flives in a hospice.
OL,17,F"When you see their face, that means a
OL,18,Flot," he said. "That means more than
OL,19,Fmoney in a way."
