OL,4,Cjackpot for good deeds
OL,6,FThe 76-year-old also used his winnings
OL,7,Fto donate #1.2 million to the Merlin
OL,8,FMultiple Scleroris Centre, in St
OL,9,FAustell, to fund a new hyrdrotherapy
OL,10,Ffor the charity.
OL,12,FMr Congdon said he made the donation
OL,13,Fin memory of his wife Rosemary, who
OL,14,Fhad multiple scelerosis and died aged
OL,15,F56.
OL,17,F"We thought it would be something
OL,18,Fnice," he said. "And it's named after
OL,19,Fher. She was called Rose and her
OL,20,Ffavourite flower was a primrose."
