OL,3,CThe Truro lottery winner using #13.5m
OL,4,Cjackpot for good deeds
OL,6,FHe added: "People come up to me in the
OL,7,Fstreet to say thank you, and that they
OL,8,Fhave family members who have been
OL,9,Fusing it who can't thank me enough."
OL,11,FSince winning the jackpot, Mr Congdon
OL,12,Fsaid he has continued to enter the
OL,13,Flottery every week and has no plans to
OL,14,Fstop.
OL,16,F"I've not had a big win again, but
OL,17,FI've had a few hundred quid here and
OL,18,Fthere," he said.
OL,20,F"At the end of the day, you've got to
OL,21,Fbe in it to win it."
